trans-unit.source: Defines an interface for a page designer component to obtain services from a designer host such as [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] at design time.
trans-unit.target: Definerer et grensesnitt for en komponent for side-designer for å hente services fra designer vert som [!INCLUDE[vsprvslong](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: All methods in this interface are to be implemented by the design host and made available to designer components through this IMobileWebFormServices interface.
trans-unit.target: Alle metodene i dette grensesnittet er implementert av verten design og gjøres tilgjengelig for designer komponenter via denne IMobileWebFormServices-grensesnittet.

trans-unit.source: Before attempting to use the methods in a custom designer component, verify that the design host actually implements the interface.
trans-unit.target: Før du prøver å bruke metoder i en egendefinert designer komponent, kan du kontrollere at utformingen verten faktisk implementerer grensesnittet.
